LICENSE INFORMATION

VirtualC64 consists of four major parts:

1. The VirtualC64 application, as provided by this repository
2. The core C64 emulator except in directory `Emulator` except reSID
3. The CPU emulator in the directory `Emulator/Components/CPU/Peddle`
4. reSID in the directory `Emulator/Components/SID/reSID`

The top-level license of the VirtualC64 project is the GNU General Public License. The core emulator and the CPU emulator are published under more liberate terms. In detail:

Component 1: VirtualC64 application
    License: GPL-3.0-or-later
             https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0.html

Component 2: Core emulator (except reSID)
    License: MPL-2.0
             https://mozilla.org/MPL/2.0

Component 3: CPU emulator (Peddle)
    License: MIT
             https://github.com/dirkwhoffmann/Peddle

Component 4: reSID
    License: GPL-2.0-or-later
             https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-2.0.html
